print(ada.mutual_names(ben))"},{"conversion_notes":"Converted a nested configuration flattener into Jac abilities. The recursive traversal is preserved, and dictionary paths are built explicitly for clarity in Jac.","jac_code":"can flatten(prefix: str, data: dict) -> dict[str, int] {
    result = {};
    for key in data {
        next_key = key;
        if prefix != "" {
            next_key = prefix + "." + key;
        }
        if data[key].__class__.__name__ == "dict" {
